        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Alex7511\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"72506\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/edb3f5/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Alex7511:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It‚Äôs a bit sad to see how little revenue there is</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>The most recent Form 990 is from two years ago, and they were just about breaking even then. With the cloud subscription now rolled out at least on Android, they should have a positive cash flow whenever the 2025 one materializes (assuming the IRS hasn‚Äôt been so defunded it‚Äôs practically abolished first).</p>",
